01:15:14,677 --> 01:15:15,815
MONTGOMERY:
Billy.

1063
01:15:15,978 --> 01:15:18,322
- A word, please.
- Clandestine.

1064
01:15:18,480 --> 01:15:21,222
- That's very funny, Mr. Wyatt.
