a lot more than you realize.

1071
01:15:36,865 --> 01:15:38,208
Oh. Okay.

1072
01:15:38,367 --> 01:15:40,608
- Is there a tux on my golden horizon?
- No. No.

1073
01:15:40,769 --> 01:15:42,180
