of this hellhole early? No offense.

1076
01:15:50,245 --> 01:15:53,124
None taken. And not exactly.
Come here.

1077
01:15:53,282 --> 01:15:55,421
I wanna show you something.

1078
01:15:55,584 --> 01:15:57,029
