1089
01:16:50,506 --> 01:16:54,477
- Well, ain't this some shit?
EARL: Goddamn movie theater.

1090
01:16:54,643 --> 01:16:57,647
- I was the brains.
- We did all the work.

1091
01:16:57,813 --> 01:16:59,383
EARL:
And he takes all the glory.

1092
01:16:59,548 --> 01:17:01,994
