01:22:46,361 --> 01:22:48,136
What was that thing
with the kid there?

1183
01:22:48,296 --> 01:22:49,673
Dad, it was nothing.

1184
01:22:50,298 --> 01:22:51,834
<i>♪ Sometimes I think ♪</i>

